&lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-GB"&gt;This
plant has been running for more than 40 years, and such a risk of explosion
during a stop of the plant was never encountered nor identified. No hazard was
defined in the hazop, neither in the risk analysis nor in the TOPS ( Yara
Technical and Operational Standard), for the neutralization section. &lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
This incident may be a lesson of learning for all fertilizer production plants.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

