&lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;" lang="EN-GB"&gt;&amp;nbsp;A
soon as the automatic fire alarm in the third floor was activated, the fire
brigade and ambulance from Her√∏ya Industrial Park was sent out to the factory.
At the same time, a heavy smoke was detected visually by an operator, and the
local plant alarm was initiated and evacuation of the building started. 10
minutes after the evacuation, an explosion occured, and five people at the
assembley area&amp;nbsp;got minor injuries from glass fragments. &amp;nbsp;Porsgrunn
Fire Brigade was callled in shortly thereafter, and worked together with the
industrial park fire brigade to extinguish the fire. The ambulance transported
2 persons to the industrial park medical unit, and they were transported to the
local hospital for further treatment. 3 other persons with minor injuries were
treated at the&amp;nbsp;industrial park medical unit.&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

